1725
01:48:27,640 --> 01:48:29,520
Gracias.

1726
01:48:29,560 --> 01:48:31,760
Cuídate, Jo.

1727
01:48:33,280 --> 01:48:37,040
Hey... Llámame.

1728
01:48:38,400 --> 01:48:40,240
Si necesitas un abogado.

1729
01:48:40,320 --> 01:48:42,760
Lo haré.

1730
01:48:42,840 --> 01:48:45,520
Y... lo haré.

1731
01:49:03,560 --> 01:49:05,400
Aeropuerto Kennedy.

1732
01:49:14,080 --> 01:49:18,040
